      "utc": "2022-05-12T20:00:00Z",
      "title": "Setting the Stage",
      "narrative": [
        "Welcome to my weather disocvery lab.  I launched with this project with the goal of bringing us back in time to some of the most extreme weather and be able to do real science by investigating the clues that made these storms so memorable.  
        This first case study takes us back to the derecho of May 12, 2022.  Imagine pulling up a chair right me as I tracked this storm live a few years ago.  You'll get that experience, with a LIVE Doppler radar simulator and even storm tracker tools that I will teach you!  I wanted this to be a unique expereience where the students get to exeperience what it's like to do my job.  I created a LIVE Doppler radar simulator and you'll see this tool often in my program.",
        
      ],
